Package virusvoid.gui.panels

package virusvoid.gui.panels
  • Klassen
    Klasse
    Beschreibung
    GamePanel
    Panel for displaying the game interface, including the planet's HP label, boss HP bar, and level announcement.
    GameTutorialEndPanel
    Panel displayed at the end of the game or tutorial, providing end messages and options to retry or go back.
    GameTutorialPanel
    Panel allowing the user to choose between starting the game (infinite game is also an option), accessing the tutorial, or returning to the main menu.
    GameTutorialSuperPanel
    The base panel for the game/tutorial, providing components for spaceship, projectiles, and animations.
    MainFrame
    The main frame for the "Virus-Void" game, providing a background panel with a scaled image.
    MainMenuPanel
    Panel representing the main menu of the "Virus-Void" game.
    OptionsPanel
    Panel representing the options menu of the "Virus-Void" game.
    OrangePanel
    A translucent orange panel used when the game/tutorial is paused.
    TutorialPanel
    Panel for displaying the tutorial interface of the "Virus-Void" game.
